suixAY srw guxw ky gwh ]
suAwmI dy nwm nUM srvx duAwrw AwdmI nykIAW dy smuMdr iv`c fUMGI cu`BI lwauNdw hY[
Listening-dive deep into the ocean of virtue.
srw guxw ky = guxW dy srovrW dy, byAMq guxW dy[ gwh = gwhux vwly, sUJ vwly, vwk&I vwly[
Akwl purK dy nwm ivc surq joVn nwl (swDwrn mnu`K) byAMq guxW dI sUJ vwly ho jWdy hn,

suixAY syK pIr pwiqswh ]
suAwmI dy nwm dw srvx krnw pRwnI nUM ivdvwn, rUhwnI rhbr Aqy bwdSwh bxw idMdw hY[
Listening-the Shaykhs, religious scholars, spiritual teachers and emperors.
