Aqy SyK pIr qy pwiqSwhW dI pdvI pw lYNdy hn[

suixAY AMDy pwvih rwhu ]
mwlk dy nwm nUM suxn duAwrw AMnHhy ienswn rsqw l`B lYNdy hn[
Listening-even the blind find the Path.
