ieh nwm suxn dI hI brkiq hY ik AMnHy igAwn-hIx mnu`K BI (Akwl purK nUM imlx dw) rwh l`B lYNdy hn[

suixAY hwQ hovY Asgwhu ]
r`b dw nwm srvx krn duAwrw AQwh swihb dI Qwih Aw jWdI hY[
Listening-the Unreachable comes within your grasp.
rwhu = rsqw[ Asgwhu = fUMGw smuMdr, sMswr[ hwQ hovY = hwQ ho jWdI hY, fUMiGAweI dw pqw l`g jWdw hY, AslIAq dI smJ pY jWdI hY[
Akwl purK dy nwm ivc juVn dw sdkw ies fUMGy sMswr-smuMdr dI AslIAq smJ ivc Aw jWdI hY[

nwnk Bgqw sdw ivgwsu ]
hy nwnk! AnurwgI hmySW AnMd mwxdy hn[
O Nanak, the devotees are forever in bliss.
